===== ABOUT =====
This library provides an easier interface to introduce Checkpoint/Restart capabilities in your program.

===== Supported types and features =====

1) POD (double, int, float etc.)
2) POD Arrays
3) GHOST dense mat
4) PHIST Mvec, SdMat 


===== REQUIREMENTS =====
1) Requires MPI

===== INSTALLATION =====
1) ccmake ./
configure according to your requirements
2) make
